metadata.name: Mankind's Marvel
metadata.description:
It is the power that lifts the world's head proudly skywards, an extraordinary union of engineering and art, the life force of collective aspirations and the aesthetic union of many cultures, the heart of Dubai and its people; the marker that defines its shining dream.

More than just a moment in time, defining moments for future generations.

This, is Burj Khalifa.

Special thanks to my brother @Web3Nullity for the creative inputs.
